Ingredients/Lactobacillus Acidophilus

Lactobacillus Acidophilus

ProbioticsEssential Capsules
Description

A probiotic bacterium that supports gut health, immune function, and nutrient absorption. One of the most well-researched probiotic strains with documented health benefits.

Molecular Formula: N/A (living organism)

Mechanism of Action

Colonizes the gut to produce lactic acid (inhibits pathogens), enhances nutrient absorption, supports gut barrier integrity, and modulates immune responses

Blueprint Dosage

20mg (4 Billion CFU)
